proposeTest
├── given escape hatch is not configured
│   └── it should use normal validator selection verification
└── given escape hatch is configured
    ├── when escape hatch is not open for current epoch
    │   └── it should use normal validator selection verification
    └── when escape hatch is open for current epoch
        ├── when caller is not the designated proposer
        │   └── it should revert with Rollup__InvalidEscapeHatchProposer
        └── when caller is the designated proposer
            ├── it should allow the proposal
            ├── it should notify escape hatch of proposal via onCheckpointProposed
            └── it should record the checkpoint normally
